data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Newport News, VA! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence boasts 1,696 square feet of living space and is move-in ready with freshly painted interior, hardwood floors, and new carpeting. Enjoy the convenience of a downstairs bedroom and the warmth of a wood-burning fireplace, great for cozy evenings. The property features a large detached garage, offering ample space for your vehicles and projects, and a fenced-in yard for privacy and security. Plus, embrace the excitement of Newport News’ downtown redevelopment, with new dining and entertainment options just moments away. Don’t miss this opportunity to live in a turn-key home where comfort meets style – schedule a showing today and make this property your own!
